        "\n",
        "Architecture:\n",
        "- **Flatten** layer: converts 28×28×1 → 784\n",
        "- **Hidden layer 1**: 64 neurons, sigmoid\n",
        "- **Hidden layer 2**: 128 neurons, sigmoid\n",
        "- **Hidden layer 3**: 256 neurons, sigmoid\n",
        "- **Output layer**: 10 neurons, softmax"
